        <head>Violenly Dedicate</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Ugly her </l>
          <l>Violently </l>
          <l>Violently delicate </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Sigh for a pretty moment </l>
          <l>Take a little bite of me </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>I ask </l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>Why couldn't I be just as delicate? </l>
          <l>Why do you have to be important? </l>
          <l>Why couldn't I be just as delicate? </l>
          <l>It doesn't have to bother my conscience </l>
          <l>Damn it </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>I can do better than this </l>
        </lg>
